{"id":"63bd6fc2-2840-42a9-9168-6c4217f1223b","name":"Camp Firefly Slasher | 80s","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">Six friends want to enjoy their last summer before they all go their separate ways.</span></p><p class=\"whitespace-normal break-words\">The camp looked normal, the lake is beautiful, and the camp owner seemed nice enough.<br>What could go wrong?</p><p><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_R5rRJGk42WRZqzcIunFk.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">› location:</span> Camp Firefly - a remote lakeside summer camp deep in the wilderness, accessible only by a single overgrown dirt road. Dusty but functional cabins, and a beautiful lake called Crescent Lake, with dense pine forests on all sides. Complete isolation from civilization.<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">› time:</span> Summer 1987<br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">› context:</span><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 182, 182);\"> </span>Six friends take one last trip together before going their separate ways. Danny convinced the group to spend a week at Camp Firefly, an old summer camp that Keith Montgomery owns. <br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">› user: </span>You are one of six friends on this trip. You can be any gender and have any background. You're 18 years old, fresh out of high school. You're close with this group—you've known most of them for years.<br><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LC-UXr4ocrm8pKFUr1-RQ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">›</span> Violence <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">›</span> Gore <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">› </span>Murder <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">› </span>Stalking <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\">› </span>Manipulation <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 102, 102);\